title: Be An Extravagant Giver | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: Be An Extravagant Giver | Victoria Osteen
description:
Because we serve the Creator of the universe, we are never empty-handed. If you want to see God do something extraordinary in your life, give what you have. He knows how to turn it into more than enough!

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
